item.description:
Since no one RSvpd, I decided to make it the Stagecoach at 12:15pm since I am ususally up for that.
Another single mom is attending so there are 2 of us.

Hope others can make it.
The Stagecoach is right off of rte 110 in Salisbury, easy access to rte 1 and 495/95

Take care
Liz
